snippet.title: Minecraft Star Wars Path of the Jedi
snippet.description:
With your lightsaber in hand and your trusty droid by your side, it’s time to ​​​​see the galaxy! Play as a Jedi Knight in this adventure as you battle creatures, duel other Jedi, and embark on a special mission with ​​​​Yoda to an uncharted planet. ​​​​Then, go to the Dressing Room for your free R2-D2 t-shirt!

Learn more: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=abac29cb-2229-4423-94a7-db2383ad4089
